  </div>
  <div class="relative border-r border-b border-l border-grey-light lg:border-l-0 lg:border-t lg:border-grey-light bg-white rounded-b lg:rounded-b-none lg:rounded-r p-4 flex flex-col justify-between leading-normal">
   
    <div class=" ">
         <Icon name="ic:baseline-plus" class="  text-lime-500 w-16 mr-5 absolute  top-0 right-0 -mt-5" />
      <p class="text-sm text-grey-dark flex  items-center">
        
        <Icon name="mdi:user-check" class=" inline-bloc  text-lime-500 w-7 mr-2" />
       <span class="text-lime-600">Gratis voordeel van de klant</span> 
      </p><div class="text-left">  
      <p class="text-grey-darker text-base text-sm"><span class="text-black font-bold text-lg">Digitale sturing </span>(bijv. app op uw smartphone) en ondersteuning bij foutmeldingen</p></div>
    
    </div>
 
  </div>
</div></div>

      

